Sometimes, you have to risk everything to discover so much more.I had to follow my heart and not my head to find the man of my dreams, and I had to do what was wrong to figure out what was right.Bryce Clark was my boss, and I was happily married -- or so I thought.He showed me what true love was and that it was worth fighting for.Now I'm living a new life with a new man and a baby on the way.We're happy.In love.Excited for what's to come.Except, not everyone shares our joy. One person lurks in the shadows, and he wants me out of Bryce's life for good.